{"tid":2396240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉用水淋內地女生指罵「大陸人」，城大女義士被控襲擊准保釋","createTime":"2021-02-05T12:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T12:07:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93f19db1ac244359d62dfa9caa61fc938c28a48f","tid":2396240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZL3MShcu36t8BwbdBBZIzw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMS4zNg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/DZ3xwkK.1.AgkhjW7d36aA--~B/aD03NDE7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/b143988887c19a2ec72a29d654ff889a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZL3MShcu36t8BwbdBBZIzw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMS4zNg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDZ3xwkK.1.AgkhjW7d36aA--~B%2FaD03NDE7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fb143988887c19a2ec72a29d654ff889a&h=c1c43072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】33歲城大本地女生去年9月涉嫌在城大圖書館，用水淋向廁格內1名不相識的內地女生，並以英文罵對方「大陸人」，被控普通襲擊。案件今早在西九龍裁判法院首次提堂，辯方申請被告毋須答辯獲准，案件押後至3月26日再訊，以待辯方索取文件及法律意見。被告獲准以500元保釋，期間不得離港，須交出旅遊證件，每周到警署報到2次。<br />\n<br />\n被告蔡詠儀被控於2020年9月15日，在香港城市大學楊建文學術樓3樓邵逸夫圖書館襲擊曾慧昭。據了解被告在去年9月被捕，獲准保釋後未有依時到警署報到被警方通緝，昨日再次被捕後，今早被押解上庭。"}]}